-- Citigroup’s Levkovich `Far More Worried’ About U.S. (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-06-22T13:09:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-22/citigroup-s-levkovich-far-more-worried-about-u-s-audio-.html
Tobias Levkovich, chief U.S. equity 
strategist at Citigroup Inc., says he is "far more worried about
the fiscal cliff" in the U.S. and its impact on investors than 
in  Europe .  Levkovich talks with Bloomberg's Ken Prewitt, Tom 
Keene and Sara Eisen on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg 
Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 10:39
 